Package: validate.adjust
Maintainer: Mark van der Loo <mark.vanderloo@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Title: Correct Numerical Data To Satisfy Linear (In)Equality Constraints
LazyData: no
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Author: Mark van der Loo, Edwin de Jonge
Description: Adjust records minimally to satisfy linear 
    (in)equality rules defined with the 'validate' package. Typical use of the methods
    implemented in this package is to adjust values that have been imputed without 
    taking the restrictions into account.
Version: 0.0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/data-cleaning/validate.adjust
BugReports: https://github.com/data-cleaning/validate.spa/issues
Date: 2015-08-28
Imports: methods, validate, supral
Suggests: testthat, knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
